						<p>This is damaged and dated the <hi rend="bold">13th year of</hi> the reign of the Yādava king <hi rend="bold">Rāmachandradēva,</hi> cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Chitrabhānu, Vaiśākha, ba. 2, Ādivāra</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1282 April 26 Sunday.</hi> It seems to record the death of a hero in a battle waged by <hi rend="bold">Basavadēva,</hi> (son of ?) <hi rend="bold">Bayirarsadēva.</hi></p>						

